==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: hóu mén shēn sì hăi
===Etymology===
From Chapter 6 of the ''[[w:Dream of the Red Chamber|Dream of the Red Chamber]]''
*Literally: The nobleman's gates are deep like the sea.
===Proverb===
# The mansions of nobility are inaccessible to the common people.
